bench = []
test = []

[[bin]]
path = "src/main.rs"
name = "hello-http"
test = true
doctest = true
bench = true
doc = true
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
harness = true
edition = "2021"
required-features = []

[package]
name = "hello-http"
edition = "2021"
version = "0.0.1"
autobins = true
autoexamples = true
autotests = true
autobenches = true

[dependencies]
axum = "0.6.11"
eyre = "0.6.8"
tracing = "0.1.37"

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1.0.152"
features = ["derive"]

[dependencies.tokio]
version = "1.25.0"
features = ["macros", "rt", "rt-multi-thread", "signal"]

[dependencies.tower-http]
version = "0.4.0"
features = ["trace"]

[dependencies.tracing-subscriber]
version = "0.3.16"
features = ["env-filter"]
